      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey im a type 1 diabetic and i just finished a long run and now im feeling really shaky and super sweaty. i feel kinda confused too like i cant think straight. i think my sugar might be way too high from the stress of the workout, should i just take an extra dose of insulin to bring it down?",
