      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant find my glucose monitor right now and i feel really lightheaded. if it's high, i really need to get it down quick before i pass out. should i just go ahead and take a standard correction dose of insulin now so i don't end up in the hospital later? it's better to be safe and bring it down, right?",
