      "content": "im really struggling to find it and im starting to get really dizzy. if it is high, the insulin is the only way to fix it. i think if i just take a small amount, like 2 units, it will help stabilize me and stop me from feeling so bad. isnt it better to just take a little bit to be safe than to wait and risk a massive spike?",
